{"TopicId":189360,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Give vernor gimbal, or a smaller sized LFO RCS thrusters","CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-28T16:57:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-28T16:57:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I know they are suppose to be vernier, but in the end, they are still bipropellent \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters v-- and we sorely need some that does not stick out so weirdly when placed perpendicular to the surface.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PositronLance001","CreatedById":197730,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-28T17:28:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlike the linear \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E jets but gimballed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-28T20:57:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223696211\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572283716\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197730\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PositronLance001\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, PositronLance001 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlike the linear \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E jets but gimballed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe best, of course, is to make it size of linear \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E AND max 45 degree Gimbals (must keep it \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Liquid Fuel and Oxidizer\u0022\u003ELFO\u003C/abbr\u003E of course), but just one of the 2 will suffice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-10-28T21:01:01Z\u0022 title=\u002210/28/2019 09:01  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 28, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Jestersage\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SnailsAttack","CreatedById":184399,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T12:34:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jestersage","CreatedById":165777,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T16:24:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223696687\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572352497\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184399\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SnailsAttack\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, SnailsAttack said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo one can place \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Liquid Fuel and Oxidizer\u0022\u003ELFO\u003C/abbr\u003E \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters that looks good, without the thrusters sticking out all over the place -- especially for aft/forward-translation \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Liquid Fuel and Oxidizer\u0022\u003ELFO\u003C/abbr\u003E \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course, if your design philosophy is \u0022I will clip everything in\u0022 or I will fly the giant spacestation wheel in one go with no fairing since i have a huge bundle of rockets\u0022, then you are right -- there is no point for that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-10-29T19:12:49Z\u0022 title=\u002210/29/2019 07:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 29, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Jestersage\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PositronLance001","CreatedById":197730,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T17:59:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223696687\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572352497\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184399\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SnailsAttack\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, SnailsAttack said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso normally the verniers look like warts (ugly).\u00A0I think they should look like the linear \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E (barely visible), and have one-direction gimbal.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}